
Steady State:
    Graph Creator():
        Once we have the steady state this function can both iterate the guess to steady state and make the graph understandable.

    Input Wrapper():
        This takes the inputs from the user and formats them to be used.

    Steady State Driver():
        Sends the user inputs to "/Steady State/Input Wrapper",
        makes and itterates a guess with "/Tesla Coil/System iterator",
        makes a graph of the steady state with "/Steady State/Graph Creater", 
        and then outputs to "../../Presentation Figures".
        The guess creater code is located here.

Tesla Coil:
    System Iterator():
        The step function for the system with a given input and step size.